#### Lists of commands  
| Command                                                                | Fungsi                                             | Status |
| ---------------------------------------------------------------------- | -------------------------------------------------- | ------ |
| `devcore login github`                                                 | Login ke GitHub (via `core/github_integration.py`) | âœ…      |
| `devcore wp setup --generate`                                          | Generate `devcore_project.json`                    | 
âœ…      |
| `devcore wp new project --type wordpress --client "New-Commerce-Project"` | Buat scaffolding baru                              | âœ…      |
| `devcore wp init New-Commerce-Project`                                 | Buat WP project baru                               | âœ…      |
| `devcore wp init New-Commerce-Project --include-setup`                 | Build project + setup plugin & theme               | âœ…      |
| `devcore config rebuild` / `config reset`                              | Reset config environment                           | âœ…      |
| `devcore wp dropdb <nama_project>`                                     | Hapus database dan folder                          | âœ…      |


