#### Notes Error fixed   
```bash
rm -rf build dist *.egg-info
pip uninstall devcore-cli -y
```  

#### Rebuild & publish  
```bash
python -m build
pip install --upgrade build
twine upload dist/*

# 1ï¸âƒ£ Bersihkan dulu build lama
rm -rf build dist *.egg-info

# 2ï¸âƒ£ Build ulang package
python setup.py sdist bdist_wheel

# 3ï¸âƒ£ Install ulang ke environment aktif
pip install --upgrade --force-reinstall dist/devcore_cli-1.0.3-py3-none-any.whl

# 1. Bersihkan build lama
rm -rf build dist *.egg-info

# 2. Build ulang
python -m build

# 3. Upload ke PyPI
twine upload dist/*

# 4. Instal versi terbaru
pip install --no-cache-dir -U devcore-cli

```  


#### Testing 
```bash
pip install --no-cache-dir -U devcore-cli
devcore --help
```

